"'''Love Long Distance'''" is the second single taken from ''[[Music for Men]]'', the fourth studio album by [[Gossip (band)|Gossip]] and was released on September 13, 2009 in the U.S.

==Track listings==
*'''Australian CD Single'''<ref>[http://www.discogs.com/Gossip-Love-Long-Distance/release/2225906 Gossip - Love Long Distance Australian CD Single] ''[[Discogs]]''. Retrieved 2010-06-09.</ref>
