# "Love Long Distance (Fake Blood Remix)" - 4:36
# "Love Long Distance (Riva Starr Remix)" - 5:56
# "Love Long Distance (Riva Starr Radio Edit)" - 3:34

*'''European CD single'''<ref>[http://www.discogs.com/Gossip-Love-Long-Distance/release/2197917 Gossip - Love Long Distance European CD Single] ''[[Discogs]]''. Retrieved 2010-06-09.</ref>
# "Love Long Distance" <U+2013> 4:24
# "Love Long Distance (Fake Blood Remix)" <U+2013> 4:36

